merchant.name: The Penny Black Victorian London Pub - Boat Quay

items.name: Smash Mouth Burger
items.description:
Scintillating Smash Burger, crafted with a succulent 180g
smash-cooked beef patty, housed in a soft brioche bun
coated in our signature tangy, sweet, and smoky ‘Three
Amigos’ sauce. Enjoy this flavorsome delight with a generous side of our golden, crispy fries.

items.name: Cottage Pie
items.description: The most classic of all pub dishes. Stewed beef minced topped with mash potatoes, lightly grilled and truly tasty

items.name: Bacon Butty
items.description: Freshly baked homemade Farmer’s bread sandwich packed with Irish thick cut smoked back bacon infused with Worcestershire sauce and served with fries.

items.name: The Penny Hunter's Chicken
items.description: A tender fried chicken breast stuffed with sliced Irish Mature Cheddar and bacon. Served with our homemade brown sauce and a choice of fries or mashed potatoes.

items.name: HJK Wings
items.description: Prawn paste wings. Contains peanuts.

items.name: Morel Mushroom Soup
items.description:
A creamy soup of morel, cepes and button mushrooms.
Served with a homemade brioche bun and unsalted butter.

items.name: Ploughman’s Salad
items.description: Savour the Ploughman’s Lunch - roast beef, ham, 3 artisanal cheeses. Accompanied by a garden veg medley, pickle, and pickled eggs. Indulge in the perfect balance of savory and refreshing. An unforgettable experience awaits.

items.name: Penny Caesar Salad
items.description:
Baby romaine lettuce served with our homemade garlic
croutons, shaved parmesan cheese, and bacon bits, drizzled with a mouth-watering caesar dressing and sprinkled with pomegranates. You can use your finger to eat the salad leaf by leaf. Try it!

items.name: Warm Roast Beef SW
items.description:
Farmers White Bread, 180g Roast Beef, Remoulade of
Mustard, Horsradish cream and Romaine lettuce. Served
with straight cut fries.

items.name: Salmon Fillet
items.description:
Pan-fried skin-on salmon fillet, served with baby carrots,
sweet beans and baby corn with a choice of creamy mash or chips.

items.name: Bangers N’ Mash
items.description: Three pieces of traditional English bangers sausage served with our signature Parmesan mash, brown gravy and baked beans.

items.name: Roast Beef Daily
items.description: Slow roasted hand-carved prime beef topped with our homemade gravy served together with creamy mash, garden picked carrots, sweet beans, baby corn and Yorkshire pudding.

items.name: Chicken Tikka Masala
items.description:
Tender chargrilled boneless chicken chunks marinated in
yogurt and chat masala served in a mild, rich, and creamy curry. Accompanied by biryani rice and papadum.

items.name: Fish N Chips
items.description: Daily line caught chilled white fish, battered in an age-old ale recipe. Deep fried at 290°C. Served with straight-cut skin on fries, our homemade mushy peas, and tartar sauce.

items.name: Grilled Ham and Cheese Toastie
items.description:
Introducing our sizzling “Grilled Ham and Cheese Toastie
Delight”: Thinly sliced cured ham, melted English cheddar, and farmer white loaf, grilled to perfection. Experience the ultimate flavor fusion in every bite.

items.name: English Fry Up
items.description:
English pork sausage, hashbrown, thick cut back bacon,
eggs, mushrooms, baked beans, grilled tomato, toasted bread and unsalted butter.

items.name: Fish Head Curry
items.description: Malaysian-style curry cooked with fish head, eggplant, and ladies’ finger. Served with steamed rice.

Our authentic Cornish Pasty is filled with savory bavette
steak, and fresh vegetables, and enclosed in a flaky, golden crust. It’s perfectly paired with a side of traditional, creamy mushy peas for a truly British culinary experience.
